Trinity::

She gave Windlord a paw's up. "heheh, Thanks." As Aerotaur still had 
her by the scruff. She looked at Nightlight who was on the 
ground. "HEy, Are you ok? You don't look so good."

She took out a small energon cube from her side compartment. "Here, I 
was saving it for a snack, but you can have it. You look like you 
need it more than me." She tossed the small cube from her paws to 
Nightlight.
